	<div class="postbody">
		
		<div class="postrow">
		
		<h2 class="posttitle icon">
			<img src="images/icons/icon1.png" alt="Default" /> 
		</h2>
		
				
				
		<div class="content">
			<div id="post_message_303013">
				<blockquote class="postcontent restore">
					Using 5400 as output slave (all rendering will be done on 7850) is impossible in your case, because:<br />
1 Proprietary drivers doesn't support DMA-BUF due to legal issues (long story). Catalyst doesn't support it too.<br />
2 Using offloading/output slaves is possible with FOSS drivers r600g (for 5400) and radeonsi (7850) but radeonsi is not quite ready.<br />
So maybe you will use (mini)DisplayPort outputs that your 7850 already have? (Sure, in this case you will need DisplayPort to HDMI/DVI adapters.)
				</blockquote>
			</div>

			


		</div>
			
